{"word":"εἰσκυκλέω","slug":"εἰσκυκλέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n31422\" key=\"ei)skukle/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">εἰσκυκλ-έω</orth>, <sense id=\"n31422.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">wheel in,</tr_> esp. in a theatre, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">turn</tr_> a thing <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">inwards by machinery,</tr_> and so, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">withdraw it from the eyes of the spectators,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg008.perseus-grc1:265\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">265</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg046:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lex.\">Lex.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8</biblScope> </bibl> : generally, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὄψων παρασκευὴν εἰσκυκλουμένην</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0008.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:27o\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ath.\">Ath.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.27o</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>e : metaph., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πράγματα δαίμων τις ἐσκεκύκληκεν ἐς τὴν οἰκίαν</foreign> some spirit <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">has wheeled</tr_> ill luck into the house, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:1475\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ V.\">V.